Following the dissolu- tion of the management of Nigeria Professional Football League side Niger Tornadoes, Niger State government has appointed Ibrahim Dada as the sole administrator of the club, BSNSports. com.ng can report. The Niger State gov- ernment dissolved the club management on Tuesday following strings of poor results recorded by the club in the ongoing season. The State govern- ment confirmed that his appointment take effect immediately as he is expected to salvage the team from relegation.